115051950.text: "Deletion of Stat3 in Jak2V617F knock-in mice significantly increased the HSC enriched LSK compartment (Lin - Sca1 + c-kit +) and its subsets including long-term HSC (LT-HSC; Lin - Sca1 + c-kit + CD34 - CD135 -), short-term HSC (ST-HSC; Lin - Sca1 + c-kit + CD34 + CD135 -), and multi-potent progenitors (MPP; Lin - Sca1 + c-kit + CD34 + CD135 +) in the BM and spleens."
